              <h2>IP Camera WebUI Setting</h2>
              <p class="text-justify">After connecting the PIR sensor with your camera’s signal input, please open the camera’s web user interface. Go to the alarm settings and activate the external alarm input:</p>
            </div>

            <div class="col-sm-12 mb">
              <div class="thumbnail" style="text-align:center">
                <img src="/images/IN-Motion500_14.png" alt="IN-Motion 500 :: INSTAR VGA WebUI" class="img-fluid img-thumbnail shadow"/>
